Colony to Be Accor Investor ‘For a Long Time,’ Le Figaro Says

-- B y   A n d r e w   R o b e r t s
-- 
2011-02-12T11:10:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-12/colony-to-be-accor-investor-for-a-long-time-le-figaro-says.html
Colony Capital LLC plans to remain a
shareholder in hotelier  Accor SA  “for a long time yet,”  Le
Figaro  reported.  The French newspaper cited Sebastien Bazin, who heads the
U.S. private-equity firm’s European operations. Accor, based in
Evry,  France , is  Europe ’s largest hotel company.  To contact the reporter on this story:  Andrew Roberts  in Paris at 
 aroberts36@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Celeste Perri at   cperri@bloomberg.net . 